# Rasm C# Testing

**Required**: `cs-testing` skill + `tests/csharp/AGENTS.md` + `tests/csharp/libs/AGENTS.md`.

## Rail split

| Rail | Owns |
|------|------|
| xUnit + `Rasm.TestKit` | Pure-managed behavior, law-matrix specs |
| `*.verify.csx` + bridge | Native Rhino/GH2 runtime paths |
| Architecture tests | Assembly dependency direction only |
| Benchmarks / fuzz | Separate executables, not xUnit |

## Oracle discipline

- Grade A/B: closed-form math, metamorphic laws, independent `Numeric` oracles
- Never mirror implementation output as expected value (Grade D)
- Use `Spec.ForAll`, `Gens`, `Numeric` from `_testkit`; promote to testkit only after ≥2 consumers
- Filtered generators: `Gen.Where(...).Select(...)` — never `Select+throw` (breaks CsCheck shrinking)
- Specs target ~175 LOC; densify with polymorphic sweeps over duplicate Facts

## Bridge scenarios

- Path: `tests/csharp/libs/<Project>/<MirrorPath>/scenarios/*.verify.csx`
- Source-only: no `#r`, `#load`, or absolute paths
- Group related checks per file (3–8s Rhino handshake each run)
- Evidence via `Console.WriteLine("key=value")`

## Validation ladder

```bash
bash scripts/test.sh
bash scripts/rhino.sh verify <scenario-or-glob>   # when bridge-owned behavior changed
```

Override target: `TEST_TARGET=<csproj> bash scripts/test.sh`
